其中，$x_{k}^{[-1]}=x_0, x_0^{[l]}=x_0, \forall k,l$，
且$V(x_k^{[l]})$是以下代数Riccati的唯一正定解
\begin{equation}
    \begin{aligned}
        V(x_k^{[l]})=Q(x_k^{[l]})+A(x_k^{[l]})^\top V(x_k^{[l]})A(x_k^{[l]})-A(x_k^{[l]})^\top V(x_k^{[l]})B(x_k^{[l]})\\
        \times\left(R(x_k^{[l]})+B^\top(x_k^{[l]})V(x_k^{[l]})B(x_k^{[l]})\right)^{-1}B^\top(x_k^{[l]})V(x_k^{[l]})A(x_k^{[l]})
    \end{aligned}
    \label{algebraic-riccati}
\end{equation}
